= Radvd =
Router advertisement daemon for IPv6.

Mostly used together with package [wiki:packages/aiccu aiccu].

Note that the subnet address prefix for sixxs should be /64, see [http://www.sixxs.net/faq/connectivity/?faq=usingsubnet&os=linux.router here].

== Links ==
 * [http://www.sixxs.net/ Sixxs.net]
 * [http://linux.die.net/man/8/radvd Man page]
